Constructor Detail

AnalyzedData

public AnalyzedData(String xName,
                    String yName,
                    double[] xData,
                    double[] yData)
Creates an instance of AnalyzedData using the specified X and Y-axis names and values.

The values of xData must be in ascending order and it is not checked.

Parameters:
xName - the name to use for the X-axis column of data.
yName - the name to use for the Y-axis column of data.
xData - the X-axis values.
yData - the Y-axis values.
